<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Jeff Speck</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/1843?language=en' lang='en'>
The walkable city
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Oct 2013
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
